[2] Global update: Polio Eradication Initiative
Date: Wed 30 Apr 2014
Source: Polio Eradication Initiative
http://polioeradication.org/Dataandmonitoring/Poliothisweek.aspx


Global Polio Eradication Initiative update as of 30 Apr 2014
------------------------------------------------------------
Wild poliovirus (WPV) cases
Total cases: Year-to-date 2014 / Year-to-date 2013 / Total 2013
Globally: 68 / 24 / 417
- in endemic countries: 59 / 24 / 160
- in non-endemic countries: 9 / 0 / 257

Case breakdown by country
Countries: 2014 WPV1 / WPV3 / W1W3 / Total 2014 // 2013 WPV1 / WPV3 / W1W3 / Total year-to-date 2013 / Total 2013 // Date most recent case

Pakistan: 54 / 0 / 0 / 54 // 6 / 0 / 0 / 6 / 93 // 6 Apr 2014
Nigeria: 2 / 0 / 0 / 2 // 16 / 0 / 0 / 16 / 53 // 24 Mar 2014
Afghanistan: 3 / 0 / 0 / 3 // 2 / 0 / 0 / 2 / 14 // 25 Feb 2014
Equatorial Guinea: 3 / 0 / 0 / 3 // 0 / 0 / 0 / 0 / 0 // 19 Mar 2014
Iraq: 1 / 0 / 0 / 1 // 0 / 0 / 0 / 0 / 0 // 10 Feb 2014
Cameroon: 3 / 0 / 0 / 3 // 0 / 0 / 0 / 0 / 4 // 31 Jan 2014
Syrian Arab Republic: 1 / 0 / 0 / 1 // 0 / 0 / 0 / 0 / 35 // 21 Jan 2014
Ethiopia: 1 / 0 / 0 / 1 // 0 / 0 / 0 / 0 / 9 // 5 Jan 2014
